{{lang|en|'''Ubuntu Touch'''}}（又稱'''Ubuntu Phone'''）是[[Canonical公司|Canonical公司]]與Ubuntu社群所開發的行動裝置作業系統<ref name=backed>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ubuntu.com/devices/backed-by-canonical |title=Backed by Canonical {{!}} Ubuntu |accessdate=2015-01-11 |archive-date=2013-03-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130326225615/http://www.ubuntu.com/devices/backed-by-canonical |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，專為[[觸控螢幕|觸控螢幕]]行動設備所設計，例如：[[智慧型手機|智慧型手機]]和[[平板電腦|平板電腦]]。现时，Ubuntu Touch 因为 Canonical 公司的[[马克·沙特尔沃思|马克·沙特尔沃思]]在 2017 年 4 月 5 日宣布该项目因为市场原因停止开发后由一个社区组织 UBports 接手并进行开发。

== 歷史 ==
2011年10月31日，[[馬克·沙特爾沃思|馬克·沙特爾沃思]]宣布推出Ubuntu 14.04時，將支援智慧型手機、平板電腦、[[智慧電視|智慧電視]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.markshuttleworth.com/archives/820 |title=Blog Archive » Ubuntu on phones, tablets, TV’s and smart screens everywhere |author=Mark Shuttleworth |date=2011-10-31 |accessdate=2013-04-08 |archive-date=2016-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160531204608/https://www.markshuttleworth.com/archives/820 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

2013年1月2日，Ubuntu平台手機亮相。<ref name=omg1>{{cite web|url=http://www.omgubuntu.co.uk/2013/01/ubuntu-phone-os-unveiled-by-canonical|title=Ubuntu Phone OS Unveiled by Canonical - OMG! Ubuntu!|author=Joey-Elijah Sneddon|work=OMG! Ubuntu!|accessdate=2014-12-23|archive-date=2021-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211231052217/https://www.omgubuntu.co.uk/2013/01/ubuntu-phone-os-unveiled-by-canonical|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=ars1>{{cite web|url=http://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2013/01/canonical-unveils-ubuntu-phone-os-that-doubles-as-a-full-pc/|title=Canonical unveils Ubuntu phone OS that doubles as a “full PC”|work=Ars Technica|accessdate=2014-12-23|archive-date=2015-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150202050650/http://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2013/01/canonical-unveils-ubuntu-phone-os-that-doubles-as-a-full-pc/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年2月21日，Ubuntu Touch開發者預覽發佈。<ref name=omg99>{{cite web|url=http://www.omgubuntu.co.uk/2013/02/ubuntu-touch-developer-preview-released-available-for-nexus-devices|title=Ubuntu Touch Developer Preview Released, Available for Nexus Devices  - OMG! Ubuntu!|author=Joey-Elijah Sneddon|work=OMG! Ubuntu!|accessdate=2014-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190518183411/https://www.omgubuntu.co.uk/2013/02/ubuntu-touch-developer-preview-released-available-for-nexus-devices|archive-date=2019-05-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

2015年2月9日，第一隻搭載Ubuntu的智慧型手機，{{link-en|Bq (廠牌)|Bq (brand)|Bq}} Aquaris E4.5在歐洲上市。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gadget-nations.net/2015/02/ubuntu-based-first-smartphone-e45-Announced.html|title=Ubuntu Based First Smartphone, Aquaris E4.5 Announced|publisher=Gadget Nations|accessdate=2015-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150209170456/http://www.gadget-nations.net/2015/02/ubuntu-based-first-smartphone-e45-Announced.html|archive-date=2015-02-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

== 發行 ==
===開發者預覽版===
開發者預覽版支援的機種包括[[三星電子|三星]]的Galaxy Nexus以及[[Google|Google]]的Nexus 4。而Ubuntu 13.10在10月發佈時，基於Qt/QML環境開發的App預計能夠正常在PC、電視、平板或智慧型手機上執行。

